# Notes:
# 1. Requires Visual C++ Redistributable: https://aka.ms/vs/17/release/vc_redist.x64.exe
# 2. Generate HTTPS certificate before starting: .\generate-https-cert.ps1
# 3. Download Bedrock Server to C:/MCBDSManager/bedrock-server/
# 4. Configure Windows Firewall:
#    - Port 8080/TCP - HTTP API
#    - Port 8081/TCP - HTTPS API
#    - Port 19132/UDP - Minecraft IPv4
#    - Port 19133/UDP - Minecraft IPv6
